translations.## Welcome to Nextcloud Talk!\nIn this c:
## Welcome to Nextcloud Talk!
In this conversation you will be informed about new features available in Nextcloud Talk.
translations.- Microsoft Edge and Safari can now be u: - Microsoft Edge and Safari can now be used to participate in audio and video calls
translations.- One-to-one conversations are now persi: - One-to-one conversations are now persistent and cannot be turned into group conversations by accident any more. Also when one of the participants leaves the conversation, the conversation is not automatically deleted any more. Only if both participants leave, the conversation is deleted from the server
translations.- You can now notify all participants by: - You can now notify all participants by posting "@all" into the chat
translations.- With the \"arrow-up\" key you can repo: - With the "arrow-up" key you can repost your last message
translations.- Talk can now have commands, send \"/he: - Talk can now have commands, send "/help" as a chat message to see if your administrator configured some
translations.- With projects you can create quick lin: - With projects you can create quick links between conversations, files and other items
translations.- You can now mention guests in the chat: - You can now mention guests in the chat
translations.- Conversations can now have a lobby. Th: - Conversations can now have a lobby. This will allow moderators to join the chat and call already to prepare the meeting, while users and guests have to wait
translations.- You can now directly reply to messages: - You can now directly reply to messages giving the other users more context what your message is about
translations.- Searching for conversations and partic: - Searching for conversations and participants will now also filter your existing conversations, making it much easier to find previous conversations
translations.- You can now add custom user groups to: - You can now add custom user groups to conversations when the circles app is installed
translations.- Check out the new grid and call view: - Check out the new grid and call view
translations.- You can now upload and drag'n'drop fil: - You can now upload and drag'n'drop files directly from your device into the chat
translations.- Shared files are now opened directly i: - Shared files are now opened directly inside the chat view with the viewer apps
translations.- You can now search for chats and messa: - You can now search for chats and messages in the unified search in the top bar
translations.- Spice up your messages with emojis fro: - Spice up your messages with emojis from the emoji picker
translations.- You can now change your camera and mic: - You can now change your camera and microphone while being in a call
translations.- Give your conversations some context w: - Give your conversations some context with a description and open it up so logged in users can find it and join themselves
translations.- See a read status and send failed mess: - See a read status and send failed messages again
translations.- Raise your hand in a call with the R k: - Raise your hand in a call with the R key
translations.- Join the same conversation and call fr: - Join the same conversation and call from multiple devices
translations.- Send voice messages, share your locati: - Send voice messages and share your location or contact details
translations.- Add groups to a conversation and new g: - Add groups to a conversation and new group members will automatically be added as participants
translations.- A preview of your audio and video is s: - A preview of your audio and video is shown before joining a call
translations.- You can now blur your background in th: - You can now blur your background in the newly designed call view
translations.- Moderators can now assign general and: - Moderators can now assign general and individual permissions to participants
translations.- You can now react to chat messages: - You can now react to chat messages
translations.- In the sidebar you can now find an ove: - In the sidebar you can now find an overview of the latest shared items
translations.- Use a poll to collect the opinions of: - Use a poll to collect the opinions of others or settle on a date
translations.- Configure an expiration time for chat: - Configure an expiration time for chat messages
translations.- Start calls without notifying others i: - Start calls without notifying others in big conversations. You can send individual call notifications once the call has started.
translations.- Send chat messages without notifying t: - Send chat messages without notifying the recipients in case it is not urgent
translations.- Emojis can now be autocompleted by typ: - Emojis can now be autocompleted by typing a ":"
translations.- Link various items using the new smart: - Link various items using the new smart-picker by typing a "/"
translations.- Moderators can now create breakout roo: - Moderators can now create breakout rooms (requires the High-performance backend)
translations.- Calls can now be recorded (requires th: - Calls can now be recorded (requires the High-performance backend)
translations.- Conversations can now have an avatar o: - Conversations can now have an avatar or emoji as icon
translations.- Virtual backgrounds are now available: - Virtual backgrounds are now available in addition to the blurred background in video calls
translations.- Reactions are now available during cal: - Reactions are now available during calls
translations.- Typing indicators show which users are: - Typing indicators show which users are currently typing a message
translations.- Groups can now be mentioned in chats: - Groups can now be mentioned in chats
translations.- Call recordings are automatically tran: - Call recordings are automatically transcribed if a transcription provider app is registered
translations.- Chat messages can be translated if a t: - Chat messages can be translated if a translation provider app is registered
translations.- **Markdown** can now be used in _chat_: - **Markdown** can now be used in _chat_ messages
translations.- Webhooks are now available to implemen: - Webhooks are now available to implement bots. See the documentation for more information https://nextcloud-talk.readthedocs.io/en/latest/bot-list/
translations.- Set a reminder on a chat message to be: - Set a reminder on a chat message to be notified later again
translations.- Use the **Note to self** conversation: - Use the **Note to self** conversation to take notes and share information between your devices
translations.- Captions allow to send a message with: - Captions allow to send a message with a file at the same time
translations.- Video of the speaker is now visible wh: - Video of the speaker is now visible while sharing the screen and call reactions are animated
translations.- Messages can now be edited by logged-i: - Messages can now be edited by logged-in authors and moderators for 6 hours
translations.- Unsent message drafts are now saved in: - Unsent message drafts are now saved in your browser
translations.- Text chatting can now be done in a fed: - Text chatting can now be done in a federated way with other Talk servers
translations.- Moderators can now ban accounts and gu: - Moderators can now ban accounts and guests to prevent them from rejoining a conversation
translations.- Upcoming calls from linked calendar ev: - Upcoming calls from linked calendar events and out-of-office replacements are now shown in conversations
translations.- Calls can now be done in a federated w: - Calls can now be done in a federated way with other Talk servers (requires the High-performance backend)
translations.- Introducing the Nextcloud Talk desktop: - Introducing the Nextcloud Talk desktop client for Windows, macOS and Linux: %s
translations.- Summarize call recordings and unread m: - Summarize call recordings and unread messages in chats with the Nextcloud Assistant
translations.- Improved meetings with recognizing gue: - Improved meetings with recognizing guests invited via their email address, import of participant lists, drafts for polls and downloading call participant lists
translations.- Schedule a meeting into your calendar: - Schedule a meeting into your calendar from within a conversation
translations.- Search for messages of the current con: - Search for messages of the current conversation directly in the right sidebar
translations.- See more conversations on a first glan: - See more conversations on a first glance with the new compact list (enable in the Talk settings)
translations.- Meeting conversations now sync the tit: - Meeting conversations now sync the title and description from the calendar and are hidden with a search filter until they are close to the start
translations.- Mark conversations as sensitive in the: - Mark conversations as sensitive in the notification settings, to hide the message content from the conversation list and notifications
translations.- To receive push notifications during \: - To receive push notifications during "Do not disturb", mark conversations as important
translations.- Add other participants to a one-to-one: - Add other participants to a one-to-one call to create a new group call on the fly
translations.- Use threads to keep your chat and disc: - Use threads to keep your chat and discussions organised
translations.- Live transcriptions now available duri: - Live transcriptions now available during the call (requires the live-transcription ExApp and the High-performance backend)

translations.**Nextcloud Talk** is a secure, self-hos:
**Nextcloud Talk** is a secure, self-hosted communication platform that integrates seamlessly with the Nextcloud ecosystem.

#### Key Features of Nextcloud Talk:

* Chat and messaging in private and group chats
* Voice and video calls
* File sharing and integration with other Nextcloud apps
* Customizable conversation settings, moderation and privacy controls
* Web, desktop and mobile (iOS and Android)
* Private & secure communication

 Find out more in the [user documentation](https://docs.nextcloud.com/server/latest/user_manual/en/talk/index.html).
translations.# Welcome to Nextcloud Talk\n\nNextcloud:
# Welcome to Nextcloud Talk

Nextcloud Talk is a private and powerful messaging app that integrates with Nextcloud. Chat in private or group conversations, collaborate over voice and video calls, organise webinars and events, customize your conversations and more.
translations.## 🎨 Format texts to create rich message:
## 🎨 Format texts to create rich messages

In Nextcloud Talk, you can use Markdown syntax to format your messages. For example, apply **bold** or *italic* formatting, or `highlight texts as code`. You can even create tables and add headings to your text.

Need to fix a typo or change formatting? Edit your message by clicking "Edit message" in the message menu.
translations.## 🔗 Add attachments and links\n\nAttach:
## 🔗 Add attachments and links

Attach files from your Nextcloud Hub using the "+" button. Share items from Files and various Nextcloud apps. Some apps even support interactive widgets, for example, the Text app.
translations.## 💭 Let the conversations flow: mention:
## 💭 Let the conversations flow: mention users, react to messages and more

You can mention everybody in the conversation by using %s or mention specific participants by typing "@" and picking their name from the list.
translations.You can reply to messages, forward them: You can reply to messages, forward them to other chats and people, or copy message content.
translations.## ✨ Do more with Smart Picker\n\nSimply:
## ✨ Do more with Smart Picker

Simply type "/" or go to the "+" menu to open the Smart Picker where you can attach various content to your messages. You can configure the Smart Picker to be able to add items from Nextcloud apps, GIFs, map locations, AI generated content and much more.
translations.## ⚙️ Manage conversation settings\n\nIn:
## ⚙️ Manage conversation settings

In the conversation menu, you can access various settings to manage your conversations, such as:
* Edit conversation info
* Manage notifications
* Apply numerous moderation rules
* Configure access and security
* Enable bots
* and more!

translations.Chat, video & audio-conferencing using W:
Chat, video & audio-conferencing using WebRTC

* 💬 **Chat** Nextcloud Talk comes with a simple text chat, allowing you to share or upload files from your Nextcloud Files app or local device and mention other participants.
* 👥 **Private, group, public and password protected calls!** Invite someone, a whole group or send a public link to invite to a call.
* 🌐 **Federated chats** Chat with other Nextcloud users on their servers
* 💻 **Screen sharing!** Share your screen with the participants of your call.
* 🚀 **Integration with other Nextcloud apps** like Files, Calendar, User status, Dashboard, Flow, Maps, Smart picker, Contacts, Deck, and many more.
* 🌉 **Sync with other chat solutions** With [Matterbridge](https://github.com/42wim/matterbridge/) being integrated in Talk, you can easily sync a lot of other chat solutions to Nextcloud Talk and vice-versa.
